            {
                "crc": "0x2fa9c963",
                "options": {},
                "comment": "/** Insert or remove a rule within a policy.\n *\n * rule_index is the 0-based position in the policy's rule vector.\n * On add, the new rule is inserted at that position (existing\n * entries pushed down). If rule_index >= current length the rule\n * is appended.\n *\n * On delete only policy_name and rule_index are consulted.\n *\n * action values match sfw_action_t (see sfw_policy_add_del).\n * address_family: 0=any 1=ip4 2=ip6. Protocol 0 means \"any\";\n * icmp_type/icmp_code 255 means \"any\".\n */"
            }
