            {
                "crc": "0x104621ad",
                "options": {},
                "comment": "/** Create or delete a NAT pool (IPv4 only in the current plugin).\n *\n * external_prefix / internal_prefix are vl_api_prefix_t (so the\n * wire encoding matches other VPP APIs) but must be IPv4 \u2014 the\n * handler rejects IPv6 for now. mode is sfw_nat_mode_t:\n *   0 = deterministic\n *   1 = dynamic\n *\n * On delete the pool whose (external_prefix, internal_prefix)\n * pair matches exactly is removed; `mode` is ignored on delete.\n */"
            }
        ],
