                "comment": "/** Create or delete a static (DNAT) mapping.\n *\n * protocol = 0 means 1:1 IP-level mapping (no port translation);\n * nonzero is TCP (6) / UDP (17) with explicit ports. Addresses are\n * vl_api_address_t on the wire but must resolve to IPv4 \u2014 the\n * plugin's NAT path is IPv4-only today.\n *\n * On delete the mapping matching (external_address, protocol,\n * external_port) is removed.\n */"
